Titolo: Persona 4: Dancing All Night

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Persona 4: Dancing All Night is a rhythm video game developed and published by Atlus for the PlayStation Vita. The game is a spin-off of the 2008 role-playing game, Persona 4, which is part of the Persona anthology of Megami Tensei games. The game was released in Japan in June 2015, in North America in September 2015, and in Europe in November 2015. A port for the PlayStation 4 was included with a limited edition bundle of Persona 3: Dancing in Moonlight and Persona 5: Dancing in Starlight.

Genere: Rhythm 

Valutazione: 76
